 in 1863]]\n[[Category:Military units and formations disestablished in 1864]]\n", "name_user": "Hhfjbaker", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eFormation", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lightning_Brigade_(US_Army_of_the_Cumberland_1863)"}
{"title_page": "Torneo Apertura 2007 (Paraguay)", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n|competition = [[Primera Divisi\u00f3n de Paraguay|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]\n|season = 2007 Apertura\n|winners = \n|relegated = \n|continentalcup1 = Copa Libertadores\n|continentalcup1 qualifiers =\n|continentalcup2 = Copa Sudamericana\n|continentalcup2 qualifiers =\n|league topscorer =\n|biggest home win =\n|biggest away win = \n|highest scoring = \n|total goals = \n|average goals = \n|longest wins = \n|longest unbeaten = \n|longest losses = \n|prevseason = [[Torneo Clausura 2006 (Paraguay)|2006 (C)]]\n|nextseason = [[Torneo Clausura 2007 (Paraguay)|2007 (C)]]\n}}\nThe '''Torneo Apertura 2007''' was the [[football (soccer)]] tournament that opened the season in the [[Liga Paraguaya: Primera Divisi\u00f3n|Paraguayan first division]] in the year 2007.\n\nThe tournament began on February 16 with the participation of 12 teams, with a two-legged [[Round-robin tournament|all play all]] system. The winner was [[Club Sportivo Luque\u00f1o|Sportivo Luque\u00f1o]], which ended a drought of championships of 54 years. <ref>[http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story?id=571615&s=gen&type=story Sportivo Luque\u00f1o gana el Torneo Apertura - ESPNdeportes.com]</ref>\n\nBy winning the Apertura, Luque\u00f1o also secured a spot for the [[Copa Libertadores 2008]] and the right to play in the national championship final against the [[Torneo Clausura 2007 (Paraguay)|Clausura 2007]] winner.\n\n==Positions==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|ptsfirst=y\n\n|team1=SLU|name_SLU=[[Club Sportivo Luque\u00f1o]]\n|team2=CER|name_CER=[[Cerro Porte\u00f1o]]\n|team3=LIB|name_LIB=[[Club Libertad]]\n|team4=OLI|name_OLI=[[2007 Club Olimpia season|Olimpia]]\n|team5=FEB|name_FEB=[[Club Atl\u00e9tico 3 de Febrero|Club 3 de Febrero]]\n|team6=NAC|name_NAC=[[Club Nacional (Paraguay)|Club Nacional]]\n|team7=TAC|name_TAC=[[Tacuary]]\n|team8=STR|name_STR=[[Sportivo Trinidense]]\n|team9=SO