 Molina]]||9||Olimpia\n|- align=center style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n| align=center |[[File:Flag of Paraguay.svg|border|20px|Paraguay]]||align=left|[[Jorge Daniel N\u00fa\u00f1ez Esp\u00ednola|Jorge N\u00fa\u00f1ez]]||8||Sportivo Luque\u00f1o\n|- align=center style=\"background:#ffffff;\"\n| align=center |[[File:Flag of Argentina.svg|border|20px|Argentina]]||align=left|[[Maximiliano Biancucchi]]||8||Sportivo Luque\u00f1o\n|- align=center style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n| align=center |[[File:Flag of Uruguay.svg|border|20px|Uruguay]]||align=left|[[Hern\u00e1n Rodrigo L\u00f3pez|Rodrigo L\u00f3pez]]||8||Libertad\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[2007 in Paraguayan football]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20080528085814/http://apf.cerocinco.net/index.php Asociaci\u00f3n Paraguaya de F\u00fatbol Website]\n* [http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/para07.html Paraguay 2007] at [[RSSSF]]\n\n{{Paraguayan Primera Divisi\u00f3n}}\n[[Category:2007 Paraguayan Primera Divisi\u00f3n season|Apertura]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n|competition = [[Primera Divisi\u00f3n de Paraguay|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]\n|season = 2007 Apertura\n|winners = \n|relegated = \n|continentalcup1 = Copa Libertadores\n|continentalcup1 qualifiers =\n|continentalcup2 = Copa Sudamericana\n|continentalcup2 qualifiers =\n|league topscorer =\n|biggest home win =\n|biggest away win = \n|highest scoring = \n|total goals = \n|average goals = \n|longest wins = \n|longest unbeaten = \n|longest losses = \n|prevseason = [[Torneo Clausura 2006 (Paraguay)|2006 (C)]]\n|nextseason = [[Torneo Clausura 2007 (Paraguay)|2007 (C)]]\n}}\nThe '''Torneo Apertura 2007''' was the [[football (soccer)]] tournament that opened the season in the [[Liga Paraguaya: Primera Divisi\u00f3n|Paraguayan first division]] in the year 2007.\n\nThe tournament began on February 16 with the participation of 12 teams, with a two-legged [[Round-robin tournament|all play all]] system. The winner was [[Club Sportivo Luque\u00f1o|Sportivo Luque\u00f1o]], which ended a drought of championships of 54 years. <ref>[http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story?id=571615&s=gen&type=story Sportivo Luque\u00f1o gana el Torneo Apertura - ESPNdeportes.com]</ref>\n\nBy winning the Apertura, Luque\u00f1o also secured a spot for the [[Copa Libertadores 2008]] and the right to play in the national championship final against the [[Torneo Clausura 2007 (Paraguay)|Clausura 2007]] winner.\n\n==Positions==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|ptsfirst=y\n\n|team1=SLU|name_SLU=[[Club Sportivo Luque\u00f1o]]\n|team2=CER|name_CER=[[Cerro Porte\u00f1o]]\n|team3=LIB|name_LIB=[[Club Libertad]]\n|team4=OLI|name_OLI=[[2007 Club Olimpia season|Olimpia]]\n|team5=FEB|name_FEB=[[Club Atl\u00e9tico 3 de Febrero|Club 3 de Febrero]]\n|team6=NAC|name_NAC=[[Club Nacional (Paraguay)|Club Nacional]]\n|team7=TAC|name_TAC=[[Tacuary]]\n|team8=STR|name_STR=[[Sportivo Trinidense]]\n|team9=SOL|name_SOL=[[Club Sol de Am\u00e9rica]]\n|team10=OCT|name_OCT=[[Club 12 de Octubre]]\n|team11=MAY|name_MAY=[[Club 2 de Mayo]]\n|team12=GUA|name_GUA=[[Club Guaran\u00ed]]\n\n|win_SLU=14|draw_SLU=5|loss_SLU=3|gf_SLU=45|ga_SLU=22\n|win_CER=13|draw_CER=4|loss_CER=5|gf_CER=42|ga_CER=18\n|win_LIB=11|draw_LIB=7|loss_LIB=4|gf_LIB=30|ga_LIB=16\n|win_OLI=10|draw_OLI=8|loss_OLI=4|gf_OLI=29|ga_OLI=21\n|win_FEB=8|draw_FEB=6|loss_FEB=8|gf_FEB=23|ga_FEB=25\n|win_NAC=6|draw_NAC=8|loss_NAC=8|gf_NAC=25|ga_NAC=23\n|win_TAC=7|draw_TAC=5|loss_TAC=10|gf_TAC=20|ga_TAC=32\n|win_STR=6|draw_STR=6|loss_STR=10|gf_STR=24|ga_STR=39\n|win_SOL=5|draw_SOL=8|loss_SOL=9|gf_SOL=19|ga_SOL=29\n|win_OCT=6|draw_OCT=5|loss_OCT=11|gf_OCT=27|ga_OCT=38\n|win_MAY=4|draw_MAY=9|loss_MAY=9|gf_MAY=24|ga_MAY=32\n|win_GUA=3|draw_GUA=7|loss_GUA=12|gf_GUA=26|ga_GUA=39\n\n|col_C=#FFD700|text_C=\n|result1=C\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n\n==Results==\n<!-- Matchday 1 y 2-->\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; float:left; margin-ri